    "As per these results, prioritizing V1, V10, and V11 while limiting the budget for V3 allows for the highest success probability (99.29%).",
    "Evaluating the correlation between each variable's cost and the project success probability allows us to rank the variables based on their cost-to-success ratio and overall significance.",
